race.comment: REINDEER HEDGHOG (5) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (26.34) last time in a Maiden H at this track. Key runner on his best form. ELECTRIC LOCH (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Geelong behind Aston Summit (26.31) in a Maiden. Has the pace to be prominent. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Leading player again. REV NATURAL (2) has mixed form recently, finishing fifth (26.34) in a Maiden H at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Well placed here and should do much better. IVORY SAKURA (8) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.
